HEADWORD: Wastebook
<hw>Waste"book`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Com.)</fld>
<def>A book in which rough entries of transactions are made, previous to
their being carried into the journal.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Wasteful</ent>⟦br⟧
